The cards matching in numerical order, but only the different colors can match. This makes the game harder. But I believe you can solve this card puzzle by […]
item.content:encoded:
One Cell is a solitaire card game. You can have fun in a poker game here. It is a little difficult, you have to match specific cards. The cards matching in numerical order, but only the different colors can match. This makes the game harder. But I believe you can solve this card puzzle by your wisdom. The Aces will be collected that can help you a little. Also, you can put a card to the free cell temporarily when you have no way to move the cards. Only you have three chances to undo the moves. If you can not figure out, only one thing you can do is restart.
drag to play

item.content:encoded:
Have you played the game Angry Birds? Neon Shot is this neon pixel style game. This is a fun physics catapult game. The game uses a very classic pixel style. Your task is to launch a ball to crash all targets. And try to collect all the coins. The ball follows the principles of physics, and its trajectory will change according to the law of reflection. Have you thought about how to launch it? If you like this game, don’t forget to share it with your friends!
Click and drag the mouse to play.

item.content:encoded:
Mathematics is one of the most complex subjects in the world. The Nobel Prize in Mathematics is awarded to those outstanding mathematics masters every year. Do you think you are good at mathematics? Math Fun Solarize is a math-related game that can test your math ability. You need to answer these math questions as soon as possible and check the scores you can get before you make a mistake. Smart kids are always good at doing math problems. If you want to exercise your calculation skills, you might as well try this game!
Mouse click or tap the screen to play.
